WEBVTT

00:00:03.000 --> 00:00:04.570
Shah Rukh Khan: When some of my friends

00:00:04.610 --> 00:00:07.110
from overseas ask me, 
"Why do Indian films sing?"

00:00:07.440 --> 00:00:09.510
I proudly ask, "Why not?"

00:00:09.830 --> 00:00:16.120
Especially since we have a treasure
trove of music, poetry and words.

00:00:16.230 --> 00:00:18.376
Today from this musical treasure trove

00:00:18.400 --> 00:00:20.209
we have a traditional classical musician

00:00:20.209 --> 00:00:24.096
and a contemporary artist, fusing
sounds to create something special.

00:00:24.884 --> 00:00:28.820
A fusion that speaks
of India’s new thought.

00:00:28.820 --> 00:00:31.796
So let’s welcome India’s
leading music arranger,